name: as her luminous heart becomes eclipsed by dark perceptions
description:
sometimes the mental darkness feels heavy and powerful, as if conquering the light within. but no darkness can overtake the light of love forever, for darkness cannot destroy light, but merely obscure it momentarily. eventually, the light of love burns through darkness and re-emerges brighter than before.

video abstraction made out of sunlight

Specs: 1892 x 1892, 00:20 seamless loop, MP4
